sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as Authentication Middleware<br/>JWT/OAuth2
    participant Quota as Quota Middleware
    participant ABAC as Access Control (ABAC)
    participant Router as Provider Router
    participant IdP as OAuth2 IdP<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SQLite as SQLite KV Store<br/>File I/O
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB (pgvector)<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Safety as Safety Provider<br/>(inline)
    participant Search as Brave Search API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 1: Chat Completion (Inference)
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth->>IdP: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>TLS 1.2+
    IdP-->>Auth: JWKS keys (cached)
    Auth-->>Server: User attributes extracted
    Server->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota->>SQLite: Read/increment counter
    SQLite-->>Quota: Quota OK (< 1000/day)
    Quota-->>Server: Allowed
    Server->>ABAC: Check resource access<br/>model::llama-3
    ABAC-->>Server: Permit
    Server->>Router: Route to inference provider
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (Bearer)
    vLLM-->>Router: Completion result (SSE stream)
    Router-->>Server: Stream tokens
    Server-->>Client: text/event-stream (SSE)<br/>Configurable TLS

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector I/O)
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/vector-io/query<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: OK
    Server->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota-->>Server: Allowed
    Server->>ABAC: Check resource access<br/>vector_db::my-docs
    ABAC-->>Server: Permit
    Server->>Router: Route to vector IO provider
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>Generate query embedding
    vLLM-->>Router: Embedding vector
    Router->>VectorDB: SELECT similarity query<br/>Auth: Username/Password<br/>Configurable TLS
    VectorDB-->>Router: Matching chunks
    Router-->>Server: Query results
    Server-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 3: Agent Turn with Tool Use
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: OK
    Server->>Router: Route to agent provider
    Router->>Safety: Run input shield<br/>(inline check)
    Safety-->>Router: Safe
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>with tool definitions
    vLLM-->>Router: tool_call: brave_search("query")
    Router->>Search: GET /search?q=query<br/>Auth: API Key<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Search-->>Router: Search results
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>with tool results
    vLLM-->>Router: Final response
    Router->>Safety: Run output shield<br/>(inline check)
    Safety-->>Router: Safe
    Router-->>Server: Stream agent response
    Server-->>Client: text/event-stream (SSE)
